question: I'm 38 weeks and I have been dizzy since last night so almost a whole day. I got my blood pressure checked and it's normal. I have gestational diabetes and my sugars are normal. I don't know what this could be but it's scaring me. I shouldn't be dizzy like this.
title: 38 weeks and dizzy
